<!-- Pharma / Life Science email body template -->
<div style="font-family: Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #333;">

<p>Hello team,</p>

{% if message_index == 0 %}
<p>I'm writing regarding <strong>{{ subject }}</strong>.</p>
<p>As we continue our research pipeline review, the following items require attention:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Phase II clinical trial enrollment status update</li>
    <li>Laboratory results review for compound DEM-{{ run_id }}-042</li>
    <li>Regulatory submission timeline alignment</li>
    <li>Research data integrity audit — quarterly checkpoint</li>
</ul>
<p>Please review the latest study protocols and provide feedback by Friday.</p>

{% elif message_index == 1 %}
<p>Thank you for the update. Here are the latest figures from the lab:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Compound DEM-042 stability data: within acceptable parameters</li>
    <li>Enrollment target: 85% achieved (340/400 participants)</li>
    <li>Adverse event rate: 2.1% (within expected range)</li>
    <li>Data monitoring committee review scheduled for next week</li>
</ul>

{% elif message_index == 2 %}
<p>Good progress on enrollment. Regulatory considerations to address:</p>
<ul>
    <li>FDA pre-submission meeting request drafted</li>
    <li>EMA parallel scientific advice — pending scheduling</li>
    <li>GLP compliance review completed — no findings</li>
</ul>

{% elif message_index == 3 %}
<p>I've completed my review of the nonclinical package and have recommendations:</p>
<ol>
    <li>Finalize the carcinogenicity study report for DEM-042 by Feb 15</li>
    <li>Schedule a cross-functional pipeline review with biostatistics</li>
    <li>Update the Investigator's Brochure to version 3 with new safety data</li>
</ol>
<p>Please confirm your availability for the review meeting next Thursday.</p>

{% elif message_index == 4 %}
<p>All confirmed from the CMC team. Manufacturing is on track:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Process validation lots — 3/3 complete, all within specification</li>
    <li>Stability study samples placed on ICH conditions</li>
    <li>Analytical method transfer to the CRO lab completed</li>
    <li>Drug substance supply secured for Phase III contingency</li>
</ul>

{% else %}
<p>Thank you all for the thorough updates. To summarize our agreed-upon next steps:</p>
<ol>
    <li>Interim analysis data lock — February 15</li>
    <li>FDA Type B meeting briefing document — first draft by March 1</li>
    <li>Updated IB distributed to all active sites by end of month</li>
    <li>Follow-up pipeline review scheduled for two weeks from today</li>
</ol>
<p>Please don't hesitate to reach out if anything comes up before then.</p>
{% endif %}

<p>Best regards</p>

<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; margin-top: 20px;" />
<p style="font-size: 11px; color: #999;">
    <em>Demo content — synthetic, no patient data. Pharma/Life Science theme.</em><br/>
    Thread: {{ thread_id }} | Message: {{ message_index + 1 }} | RunId: {{ run_id }}
</p>
</div>
